Invocation Name: its supernatural
Developer Terms of Use
des:
It's Supernatural! deals with subjects that most shy away from in this seeker-sensitive age. It emphasizes the supernatural, biblical viewpoint that the secular networks do not understand. And at the end of each program, host, Sid Roth, tells the viewers how they can have intimacy with God.

Once enabled, you can listen to the most recent episode by saying, "Alexa, play It’s Supernatural!"

To pause or resume any episode, say "Alexa, pause" or "Alexa, resume." To listen to previous episodes, say "Alexa, play the previous episode." If you want to know the title of an episode while the episode is playing, say "Alexa, ask It’s Supernatural! for the title of this episode." If you want to know the air date of an episode, say "Alexa, ask It’s Supernatural! for the date of this episode."
